00:01:54.020 --> 00:01:58.020
[Amit Varma]: it documents migrations out of India, into India and within India

00:01:58.020 --> 00:02:02.020
[Amit Varma]: and tells a story of a society that has always been in flux

00:02:02.020 --> 00:02:04.020
[Amit Varma]: it's a riveting read as a book of history

00:02:04.020 --> 00:02:07.020
[Amit Varma]: and it also carries much sociological insight

00:02:07.020 --> 00:02:09.020
[Amit Varma]: into what makes us what we are

00:02:09.020 --> 00:02:13.020
