[Amit Varma]: people

00:20:20.020 --> 00:20:21.020
[Amit Varma]: who

00:20:21.020 --> 00:20:22.020
[Amit Varma]: actually

00:20:22.020 --> 00:20:23.020
[Amit Varma]: wanted to

00:20:23.020 --> 00:20:24.020
[Amit Varma]: leave

00:20:24.020 --> 00:20:25.020
[Amit Varma]: the

