[Amit Varma]: country

00:20:26.020 --> 00:20:27.020
[Amit Varma]: were

00:20:27.020 --> 00:20:28.020
[Amit Varma]: also

00:20:28.020 --> 00:20:29.020
[Amit Varma]: suffering

00:20:29.020 --> 00:20:30.020
[Amit Varma]: from

00:20:30.020 --> 00:20:31.020
[Amit Varma]: these

